# xtool Documentation Sync

## Update Triggers
- Completion of quality gates or E2E tests.
- Updates to project phases, operational procedures, or troubleshooting guides.
- Detection of failures caused by external specification changes.

## Target Files
- `docs/release_preflight_checklist.md`
- `docs/quality_gate_routine.md`
- `docs/troubleshoot_guide.md`
- `docs/refactor_phase_ledger.md`
- `docs/external_spec_changes.md`

## Documentation Standards
- Record date, command, and result (pass/fail).
- Maintain terminology consistency.
- For external spec changes, immediately document "what changed" and "workarounds."